name: Honey Bee 6' Leash
description:
Honey Bee Leash

Gypsy Girl Leashes are made with:

•	100% cotton fabric with a Nylon Wedding backer
•	Welded nickel plated Spring Return Barrel Snap Hooks.  
•	UV resistant threads (Used in making sails).

Gypsy Girl Creations Leashes are durable and constructed to last, however, to ensure the safety of your pet, it is important that you periodically check your dog's leash for signs of wear and replace when necessary. As with most fabrics, leashes will wear with frequent use and washings. 

Leashes should be hand washed in cold water and line dried for cleaning*. For stubborn stains, pretreat with Spray "N Wash. To provide extra protection between washings, treat with Scotchgard spray.

Each leash is hand made by me and will vary slightly from the picture due to pattern placement on the fabric at the time of cutting.

name: Purple and Paisley Collar
description:
Purple and Paisley Collar

Gypsy Girl Collars are made with:
• 100% cotton fabric with a Nylon Wedding backer
• Welded nickel plated D and O rings. They will not “Open”.
• “Wide Mouth” Triglides to allow easy adjustments on the neck and body.
• Contoured buckles designed for a comfortable fit.
• UV resistant threads (Used in making sails).

Before you order please measure your pets neck and confirm that his or her measurements will fit the collar you choose. If you have any questions or concerns about the fit I encourage you to visit our (Size Charts Page) or feel free to contact me.  I will be happy to make a custom fit just for you. Your complete satisfaction is important.

Gypsy Girl Creations Collars are durable and constructed to last, however, to ensure the safety of your pet, it is important that you periodically check your dog's collar for signs of wear and replace when necessary. As with most fabrics, collars will wear with frequent use and washings. 

Collars hhould be hand washed in cold water and line dried for cleaning*. For stubborn stains, pretreat with Spray "N Wash. To provide extra protection between washings, treat with Scotchgard spray.

Each one is made by me and each collar will vary slightly from the picture due to pattern placement on the fabric at the time of cutting.
